==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Refel
<hw>Re*fel"</hw> <pr>(r?*f?l")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>refellere</ets>; pref. <ets>re-</ets> re- + <ets>fallere</ets> to
deceive.]</ety> <def>To refute; to disprove; <as>as, to <ex>refel</ex>
the tricks of a sophister</as>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>How he <qex>refelled</qex> me, and how I replied.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Refer</ent>⟦br⟧
